to drop by the film set?

374
00:15:34,965 --> 00:15:36,426
I'll do as you say.

375
00:15:36,486 --> 00:15:37,005
Okay.

376
00:15:37,006 --> 00:15:38,346
You can come in the afternoon.

377
00:15:38,406 --> 00:15:39,045
All right.

378
00:15:39,046 --> 00:15:40,045
See you then.

379
00:15:40,046 --> 00:15:40,485
Okay.

380
00:15:40,486 --> 00:15:41,426
Goodbye.

381
00:15:55,006 --> 00:15:55,946
Come in.

382
00:15:59,845 --> 00:16:00,666
Boss.

383
00:16:00,685 --> 00:16:02,145
Why are you looking for me?

384
00:16:07,605 --> 00:16:09,385
I need you to investigate something.

385
00:16:10,046 --> 00:16:10,885
Go on.

386
00:16:10,886 --> 00:16:12,745
I'm good with investigation.

387
00:16:12,766 --> 00:16:14,225
What do you want to investigate?

388
00:16:14,621 --> 00:16:15,924
Lingling has a brother.

389
00:16:15,925 --> 00:16:17,186
His name is Song Chongming.

390
00:16:17,366 --> 00:16:19,946
He passed away
in an accident when she was little.

391
00:16:20,886 --> 00:16:22,604
I need you to find out

392
00:16:22,605 --> 00:16:23,245
more details

393
00:16:23,246 --> 00:16:25,225
about the car accident.

394
00:16:25,406 --> 00:16:27,186
I want the details.

395
00:16:27,486 --> 00:16:28,826
Well.

396
00:16:28,886 --> 00:16:31,625
This happened years ago.

397
00:16:32,085 --> 00:16:32,964
Well?

398
00:16:32,965 --> 00:16:33,985
Is it tough?

399
00:16:34,725 --> 00:16:35,485
No.

400
00:16:35,486 --> 00:16:36,625
I'll think of a way.

401
00:16:40,126 --> 00:16:41,265
But Boss,

402
00:16:41,325 --> 00:16:43,186
if you don't mind me asking.

403
00:16:43,646 --> 00:16:46,225
Why do you want to investigate the case?

404
00:16:46,366 --> 00:16:48,706
Did Goddess Lanyao tell you something?

405
00:16:48,845 --> 00:16:51,045
You seemed upset

406
00:16:51,046 --> 00:16:52,505
when you came back earlier.

407
00:16:52,925 --> 00:16:54,365
Did you two have a fight

408
00:16:54,366 --> 00:16:55,466
because of this?

409
00:16:56,886 --> 00:16:58,466
I'm just worried about her.

410
00:16:59,166 --> 00:17:01,225
She hasn't moved on.

411
00:17:01,366 --> 00:17:03,045
Hence, she's very attached

412
00:17:03,046 --> 00:17:04,506
to the Brother character.

413
00:17:05,686 --> 00:17:06,826
I know.

414
00:17:06,966 --> 00:17:08,986
This is putting her
in a difficult position.

415
00:17:09,325 --> 00:17:10,404
I don't wish to see her

416
00:17:10,405 --> 00:17:12,105
struggling and suffering.

417
00:17:13,246 --> 00:17:15,986
She never told me about the incident.

418
00:17:16,446 --> 00:17:17,425
Hence,

419
00:17:17,766 --> 00:17:20,066
I want to find out myself.

420
00:17:20,325 --> 00:17:21,266
Perhaps

421
00:17:21,486 --> 00:17:23,506
I can help her untie her regrets.

422
00:17:25,325 --> 00:17:26,346
Boss.

423
00:17:26,686 --> 00:17:28,205
I never expect

424
00:17:28,206 --> 00:17:30,465
that you'd do this for a girl.

425
00:17:30,486 --> 00:17:32,385
You're indeed incredible.

426
00:17:33,085 --> 00:17:34,604
As your employee

427
00:17:34,605 --> 00:17:35,986
and as your buddy,

428
00:17:36,325 --> 00:17:37,465
you have my support.

429
00:17:38,165 --> 00:17:39,105
I mean it.

430
00:17:49,966 --> 00:17:52,105
I bought a flight ticket
to France tomorrow.

431
00:17:54,645 --> 00:17:56,586
Why must you leave?

432
00:18:01,885 --> 00:18:04,105
Your family is against our relationship.

433
00:18:05,125 --> 00:18:06,905
We won't end up well.

434
00:18:08,325 --> 00:18:09,826
I only know one thing,
which is I love you.

435
00:18:10,686 --> 00:18:12,105
Isn't that enough?

436
00:18:12,686 --> 00:18:13,905
I know.

437
00:18:14,046 --> 00:18:15,506
I love you too.

438
00:18:18,246 --> 00:18:20,625
But marriage is different.

439
00:18:20,966 --> 00:18:22,844
Do you think that our love

440
00:18:22,845 --> 00:18:24,346
is all we need?

441
00:18:26,286 --> 00:18:27,986
How long can

442
00:18:28,325 --> 00:18:30,346
a love without blessing last?

443
00:18:31,286 --> 00:18:32,266
One year?

444
00:18:33,246 --> 00:18:34,346
Five years?

445
00:18:35,085 --> 00:18:36,346
Ten years?

446
00:18:36,805 --> 00:18:38,385
Or our whole lives?

447
00:18:39,645 --> 00:18:41,826
Marriage is a matter
between two families.

448
00:18:42,125 --> 00:18:44,324
Your family is against our relationship.

449
00:18:44,325 --> 00:18:46,306
How can we be happy?

450
00:18:47,206 --> 00:18:48,965
We can leave them.

451
00:18:48,966 --> 00:18:50,665
We don't have to mind them.

452
00:18:52,165 --> 00:18:54,465
Will you bear to cut off ties with them?

453
00:18:56,125 --> 00:18:58,404
Can you bear to let your aging parents

454
00:18:58,405 --> 00:19:00,226
take care of themselves on their own?

455
00:19:05,926 --> 00:19:07,306
I don't blame you.

456
00:19:08,845 --> 00:19:10,665
I'm just begging you.

457
00:19:12,405 --> 00:19:15,266
Before we fall deeper in love,

458
00:19:16,325 --> 00:19:17,586
while

459
00:19:18,165 --> 00:19:20,826
we can still endure the pain,

460
00:19:22,726 --> 00:19:24,306
we should let each other go.

461
00:19:30,125 --> 00:19:32,586
But I can't bear to break up with you.

462
00:19:33,125 --> 00:19:35,066
Me too.

463
00:19:36,325 --> 00:19:36,725
Let her go.

464
00:19:36,726 --> 00:19:37,625
Let her go.

465
00:19:37,766 --> 00:19:38,945
What are you doing?

466
00:19:40,085 --> 00:19:41,164
Who are you?

467
00:19:41,165 --> 00:19:42,465
I'm her boyfriend.

468
00:19:42,526 --> 00:19:43,644
Cut.

469
00:19:43,645 --> 00:19:44,644
What's happening?

470
00:19:44,645 --> 00:19:45,705
Where's the supervisor?

471
00:19:46,325 --> 00:19:46,644
Hold on.

472
00:19:46,645 --> 00:19:48,364
Hang on.

473
00:19:48,365 --> 00:19:49,324
Calm down.

474
00:19:49,325 --> 00:19:50,629
We're just acting.

475
00:19:50,630 --> 00:19:51,970
I don't care.

476
00:19:52,325 --> 00:19:53,324
Take him away.

477
00:19:53,325 --> 00:19:54,425
Are you still filming or not?

478
00:19:54,805 --> 00:19:55,965
I'm so sorry, Mr. Zhang.

479
00:19:55,966 --> 00:19:56,884
Let me settle this.

480
00:19:56,885 --> 00:19:57,604
Come here.

481
00:19:57,605 --> 00:19:58,485
What are you doing?

482
00:19:58,486 --> 00:19:59,625
Come here.

483
00:19:59,966 --> 00:20:00,865
Hurry up.

484
00:20:11,885 --> 00:20:13,084
What are you trying to do?

485
00:20:13,085 --> 00:20:14,185
Go home with me.

486
00:20:15,006 --> 00:20:16,285
I still have work to do here.

487
00:20:16,286 --> 00:20:17,000
I can't leave.

488
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:19,285
So, are you going
to continue with the filming?

489
00:20:19,286 --> 00:20:20,324
Of course.

490
00:20:20,325 --> 00:20:21,905
I've signed the agreement.

491
00:20:22,085 --> 00:20:23,364
If I leave now,

492
00:20:23,365 --> 00:20:24,865
I'll need to pay the compensation.

493
00:20:25,325 --> 00:20:26,465
Liu Yiyi.

494
00:20:26,686 --> 00:20:28,625
I can support you financially.

495
00:20:28,686 --> 00:20:31,625
Why are you using
your beauty to make a living?

496
00:20:42,365 --> 00:20:44,746
You think that I'm using my beauty?

497
00:20:48,325 --> 00:20:50,306
You know that's not what I meant.

498
00:20:55,446 --> 00:20:57,266
You really look down on me, don't you?

499
00:20:59,286 --> 00:21:00,625
Unlike you,

500
00:21:01,165 --> 00:21:02,786
I didn't come from a wealthy family.

501
00:21:03,885 --> 00:21:05,644
I just want to make a living

502
00:21:05,645 --> 00:21:06,826
by myself.

503
00:21:08,486 --> 00:21:10,685
You must have felt superior

504
00:21:10,686 --> 00:21:12,625
and looked down on us peasants.

505
00:21:14,526 --> 00:21:16,205
I'm not looking down on you.

506
00:21:16,206 --> 00:21:18,826
I just can't see you working like that.

507
00:21:21,165 --> 00:21:22,506
Listen,

508
00:21:22,926 --> 00:21:25,346
I must finish my work today.

509
00:21:31,365 --> 00:21:32,245
Mr. Zhang.

510
00:21:32,246 --> 00:21:33,525
Please don't be upset.

511
00:21:33,526 --> 00:21:34,364
I'm really sorry.

512
00:21:34,365 --> 00:21:35,644
I'm sorry, everyone.

513
00:21:35,645 --> 00:21:36,364
I'm sorry.

514
00:21:36,365 --> 00:21:37,765
I'm so sorry, Mr. Zhang.

515
00:21:37,766 --> 00:21:40,625
I've caused a delay
in the filming process. I'm really sorry.

516
00:21:41,565 --> 00:21:43,084
I told you.

517
00:21:43,085 --> 00:21:44,445
She's an influencer, she cannot act.

518
00:21:44,446 --> 00:21:45,564
She cannot act.

519
00:21:45,565 --> 00:21:46,644
Can we still film now?

520
00:21:46,645 --> 00:21:47,525
I'm sorry.

521
00:21:47,526 --> 00:21:48,625
I'm sorry.

522
00:21:50,766 --> 00:21:52,185
Whatever. Let's wrap up.

523
00:21:52,845 --> 00:21:53,564
Mr. Zhang.

524
00:21:53,565 --> 00:21:54,525
It's my problem.

525
00:21:54,526 --> 00:21:56,205
Can you give me another chance?

526
00:21:56,206 --> 00:21:57,306
Mr. Zhang.

527
00:21:58,405 --> 00:21:59,485
Mr. Zhang.

528
00:21:59,486 --> 00:22:01,145
Please give her another chance.

529
00:22:01,845 --> 00:22:02,945
Mr. Zhang.

530
00:22:07,885 --> 00:22:09,285
Everyone, let's do another shot.

531
00:22:09,286 --> 00:22:10,965
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

532
00:22:10,966 --> 00:22:12,105
I'm so sorry.

533
00:22:19,206 --> 00:22:19,925
Why

534
00:22:19,926 --> 00:22:22,625
