537
00:22:27,845 --> 00:22:29,285
I don't think so.

538
00:22:29,286 --> 00:22:30,385
Let me have a guess.

539
00:22:30,405 --> 00:22:32,306
You just want to have a date with me.

540
00:22:33,125 --> 00:22:34,465
Why are you laughing?

541
00:22:35,446 --> 00:22:37,105
I think

542
00:22:37,845 --> 00:22:38,945
