544
00:22:41,526 --> 00:22:43,105
I've always been cute.

545
00:22:43,446 --> 00:22:44,804
You should be grateful

546
00:22:44,805 --> 00:22:46,145
to have a girlfriend like me.

547
00:22:47,726 --> 00:22:49,425
But I'm really curious.

548
00:22:49,605 --> 00:22:51,546
Are you always this carefree?

549
00:22:53,006 --> 00:22:54,066
Well, I do have troubles.

550
00:22:54,246 --> 00:22:57,786
In primary school,
I was concerned about my height.

551
00:22:58,246 --> 00:22:59,525
In high school,

552
00:22:59,526 --> 00:23:01,586
I was worried about my breakouts.

553
00:23:01,726 --> 00:23:03,665
After graduating from college,

554
00:23:03,805 --> 00:23:05,826
I worried about why you didn't like me.

555
00:23:07,486 --> 00:23:09,066
You have quite a lot of troubles.

556
00:23:09,405 --> 00:23:10,945
However,

557
00:23:11,006 --> 00:23:12,145
it's very specific.

558
00:23:13,526 --> 00:23:15,465
Are you laughing at me?

559
00:23:18,165 --> 00:23:19,285
However,

560
00:23:19,286 --> 00:23:22,066
I'm still very ambitious.

561
00:23:22,686 --> 00:23:24,925
My biggest concern

562
00:23:24,926 --> 00:23:26,765
is whether Xiao Ran
can get the copyright

563
00:23:26,766 --> 00:23:29,226
